00:09:15.370 --> 00:09:18.049
the Bible every day.

00:09:18.049 --> 00:09:19.649
And then what about the next step?

00:09:20.610 --> 00:09:23.769
We want our students also to be able to prepare

00:09:23.769 --> 00:09:25.490
